Name: uuid
Description: IDs made by combining puuid and match id for SQL data base

Name: matchId
Description: Match ID provided from riot API

Name: participants
Description: Gives a list of the puuids for each player in a match

Name: puuid
Description: "Player Universally Unique IDentifiers" riots way of identifiying every player

Name: endOfGameResult
Description: Shows if the game was completed

Name: gameCreation
Description: Time that the game was created in ms

Name: gameDuration
Description: How long the game lasted in seconds

Name: gameEndTimestamp
Description: Time stamp for when the game ended in ms

Name: gameId
Description: ID for each game

Name: patch
Description: Patch the game was played on

Name: riotIdGameName
Description: Name of the riot account of the player

Name: riotIdTagline
Description: Tagline of the player

Name: summonerName
Description: League of Legends in game name

Name: kills
Description: Number of kills player had

Name: deaths
Description: Number of deaths player had

Name: assists
Description: Number of assists player had

Name: firstBloodKill
Description: Checks to see if player got first blood

Name: firstBloodAssist
Description: Checks to see if player assisted in getting the first blood

Name: doubleKills
Description: How many double kills the player got

Name: tripleKills
Description: How many triple kills the player got

Name: quadraKills
Description: How many quadra kills the player got

Name: pentaKills
Description: How many penta kills the player got

Name: unrealKills
Description: How many unreal kills the player got

Name: largestMultiKill
Description: Largest multi kill (penta, quadra, etc.) player got that game

Name: killingSprees
Description: How many times player killed three champions in a row without dying

Name: largestKillingSpree
Description: How many champions player killed before dying

Name: teamKills
Description: Total number of kills player team has

Name: timePlayed
Description: Total amount of time played in seconds

Name: longestTimeSpentLiving
Description: Longest time spent alive in seconds

Name: totalTimeSpentDead
Description: Total amount of time spent dead in seconds

Name: perctTimeDead
Description: Percentage of time dead in match

Name: cs
Description: Creep Score

Name: neutralMinionsKilled
Description: How many netural minons were killed (scuttle crabs, void grubs, baron, dragons, etcs.)

Name: totalAllyJungleMinionsKilled
Description: How many allied jungle camps that were killed

Name: totalEnemyJungleMinionsKilled
Description: How many enemy jungle camps that were killed

Name: OMWPing
Description: Number of On my way pings player used

Name: allInPings
Description: Number of all in pings player used

Name: assistMePings
Description: Number of assist me pings player used

Name: enemyMissingPings
Description: Number of enemy missing pings player used

Name: enemyVisionPings
Description: Number of enemy vision pings player used.

Name: holdPings
Description: Number of hold pings player used.

Name: getBackPings
Description: Number of get back pings player used.

Name: needVisionPings
Description: Number of need vision pings player used.

Name: pushPings
Description: Number of push pings player used.

Name: visionScore
Description: Total vision score player had

Name: visionClearedPings
Description: Number of vision cleared player used

Name: visionWardsBoughtInGame
Description: How many vision wards were bought in the game by player

Name: wardsKilled
Description: How many enemy wards were killed by the player

Name: wardsPlaced
Description: How many wards the player placed

Name: sightWardsBoughtInGame
Description: How many control wards the player bought

Name: detectorWardsPlaced
Description: How many contorl wards the player placed

Name: baronKills
Description: How many baron kills the player had

Name: dragonKills
Description: How many dragon kills the player had

Name: damageDealtToObjectives
Description: Total damage dealt to objective by player

Name: objectivesStolen
Description: Number of objective stolen by player

Name: objectivesStolenAssists
Description: Number of assists in stealing objective by player

Name: turretKills
Description: Number of turrets killed by player

Name: turretTakedowns
Description: Number of turrets taken down by player (same as above)

Name: turretsLost
Description: Number of turrets that the team lost

Name: firstTowerAssist
Description: Did the player assist in taking the first turret

Name: firstTowerKill
Description: Did the player take the first turret

Name: damageDealtToBuildings
Description: Total amount of damage player dealt to buildings

Name: damageDealtToTurrets
Description: Total amound of damage player did to turret

Name: inhibitorKills
Description: Total number of inhibitor kills

Name: inhibitorTakedowns
Description: Same as above

Name: inhibitorsLost
Description: Number of inhibitors that player's team lost

Name: teamPosition
Description: Player lane position

Name: lane
Description: Player lane position

Name: role
Description: Player lane position

Name: championName
Description: Name of champion that the player played

Name: champExperience
Description: Amount of experience that player had

Name: champLevel
Description: The level that the player ended the game with

Name: championTransform
Description: This field is currently only utilized for Kayn's transformations. (Legal values: 0 - None, 1 - Slayer, 2 - Assassin)
